query:
SELECT u.id, u.name, u.email, u.role, u.accountStatus, m.id as member_id, m.membershipTier, m.userId 
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN members m ON u.id = m.userId 
WHERE u.name LIKE '%doublecranch%' OR u.email LIKE '%doublecranch%';
